com.camerontec.util.io.socket

Interface SelectableChannelReadProcessor<T extends SelectableChannelReference>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The channel reference type.

    public interface SelectableChannelReadProcessor<T extends SelectableChannelReference>
    Interface to be implemented by input socket channel processors which are registered with a SelectableChannelReadMultiplexer.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      int readAndProcess(T channel)
      Read and process bytes from the specified channel.

    • Method Detail

      • readAndProcess

        int readAndProcess(T channel)
        Read and process bytes from the specified channel.

        This method should not throw. If it does the channel may be forcibly disconnected and de-registered without notice.

        Parameters:
        channel - The channel.
        Returns:
        The number of bytes read from the channel. A value <0 means the channel is disconnected.
